    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >回忆山谷</h2><br>在免费大型更新《回忆山谷》中享受 6 小时的全新游戏内容，扩展巴辛姆的故事，探索绝美的新地区——埃尔奥拉。完整版游戏也会得到多方面改进。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/8f8f81bc61442be7af1427d6bc7f2b97.poster.avif?t=1766087993\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/8f8f81bc61442be7af1427d6bc7f2b97.webm?t=1766087993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >终极刺客</h2><br>成为系列史上最多才多艺、本领高强的刺客。在城市中流畅跑酷，利用各种当时最先进的道具。在刺客据点接受委托并完成升级，收集关键线索，以前所未有的凶猛技艺灭敌于无形。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/86bb4599b7986bdcfcd4866107597dd2.poster.avif?t=1766087993\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/86bb4599b7986bdcfcd4866107597dd2.webm?t=1766087993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/86bb4599b7986bdcfcd4866107597dd2.mp4?t=1766087993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >致敬系列本源</h2><br>系列史上牵动无数玩家的经典玩法与功能，将在本作中再度革新。前往刺客组织传说中的家园——阿拉穆特，追寻信条的本源，向《刺客信条》最初作致敬。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/a72780e14b01f5ea7ce2096e5f9a04b6.poster.avif?t=1766087993\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/a72780e14b01f5ea7ce2096e5f9a04b6.webm?t=1766087993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/a72780e14b01f5ea7ce2096e5f9a04b6.mp4?t=1766087993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >身临其境、感受城市气息</h2><br>在这座生机勃勃的宏伟城市中，每位市民都会对你的一举一动做出反应。从产业蓬勃的卡尔克，到绿意盎然的圆城，揭开四片区域隐藏的独特秘密。探索出人意料的世界事件，与塑造巴格达黄金时代的历史名人亲身交流。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/9f6e7dfac607e6db6ddd25a9dc3d86b1.poster.avif?t=1766087993\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/9f6e7dfac607e6db6ddd25a9dc3d86b1.webm?t=1766087993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/9f6e7dfac607e6db6ddd25a9dc3d86b1.mp4?t=1766087993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >见证震撼的角色蜕变</h2><br>跟随巴辛姆的脚步，踏上一段制作精巧、着重叙事的动作冒险体验。交友、拜师、树敌，看他如何从年轻小贼一步步成长为刺客大师，塑造自己的命运。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/5248e1f5b73463d3339ca23bdd0fcb03.poster.avif?t=1766087993\" width=600 height=345 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035570/extras/5248e1f5b73463d3339ca23bdd0fcb03.webm?t=1766087993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
